  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, in this way, technology becomes something hostile to humankind-something that is changing the conditions of living.",
    "It is not either/or generative AI or an author.",
    "Rather, the relationship between generative AI and human authorship is best understood as a collaborative and integrative process which is happening in the certain societal field.",
    "This collaboration recognizes that while generative AI can assist in the production and refinement of text, it is the human author who provides the essential context, critical analysis, and domain-specific knowledge necessary for meaningful scientific communication.",
    "As we referred to previously, this goes beyond the distinction between the deterministic approach to technology and instrumentalism, that is that technology, such as generative AI is an external influence on society or as a tool for humanity."
